                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/4400" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0621</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9486 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Earn-out”支付：并购商誉减值的“缓冲垫”</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“Earn-out” Payment: “Buffer” for the Impairment of Goodwill</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">方慧，李锦涛</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">上海大学MBA教育管理中心</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">北京蓝色光标数据科技股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">服务业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">12 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">企业并购；商誉减值；Earn-out支付；或有对价；公允价值</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Corporate Mergers and Acquisitions, Impairment of Goodwill, Earn-out Payment, Contingent Consideration, Fair Value</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019年4月30日，是上市公司2018年年报披露的截止日期，多家上市公司的业绩集中爆雷，其中最重要的原因就是商誉大幅减值，一时间广大投资者谈“商誉”而色变，据统计，截至2018年9月，我国资本市场上已经积累了1.45万亿的商誉，随着大量被并购企业纷纷未完成业绩承诺，悬在A股头顶上的这把“达摩克里斯之剑”让整个资本市场战战兢兢。而蓝色光标在2013年底收购WAVS公司时最早所采用的“Earn-out”支付方式，不仅化解了估值风险，成功完成了对WAVS的收购，并在WAVS出现未完成承诺业绩时成功实现了对并购商誉减值的有效缓冲，无疑值得各大企业在并购过程中借鉴和学习。本案例以蓝色光标收购WAVS公司为研究对象，介绍了Earn-out支付方式在企业并购中的运用，旨在引导广大学员理解和掌握企业并购中“Earn-out”支付方式运用及其会计处理，同时思考其会计处理方式如何能对巨额商誉减值损失起到缓冲作用，开拓学员的会计视野，让学员对并购支付方式及其会计处理的相关问题有更加全面的认识。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">April 30, 2019, is the deadline for the disclosure of listed companies&#39; 2018 annual reports. The performance of many listed companies is concentrated in thunder. The most important reason is that the goodwill is greatly reduced. At one time, investors talk about &quot;goodwill&quot;. According to statistics, as of September 2018, China’s capital market has accumulated 1.45 trillion goodwill. With a large number of M&amp;A companies failing to fulfill their performance commitments, this “Dharma” hanging above the A-share market The Chris Sword makes the entire capital market tremble. The “Earn-out” payment method adopted by Blue Cursor when it acquired WAVS at the end of 2013 not only solved the valuation risk, but also successfully completed the acquisition of WAVS, and successfully realized the unfulfilled commitment performance of WAVS. The effective buffer of the impairment of mergers and acquisitions is undoubtedly worth learning and learning from the major companies in the process of mergers and acquisitions. This case is based on the acquisition of WAVS by Blue Cursor. It introduces the application of Earn-out payment method in enterprise mergers and acquisitions. It aims to guide the students to understand and master the application of “Earn-out” payment method and its accounting treatment in enterprise mergers and acquisitions. At the same time, think about how its accounting treatment can buffer the huge loss of goodwill impairment, open up the accounting horizons of the students, and let the students have a more comprehensive understanding of the M&amp;A payment methods and related issues of accounting treatment.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2019</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《高级财务会计理论与实务》、《公司财务》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">并购业绩补偿机制、“Earn-out”</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2020-03</td>
                            </tr>
